latestPosts.caption: The beautiful angel who made me a mom: Everything I’m working toward, every bit of growth and healing—it’s all for you. You changed my life in the most beautiful, powerful way, and I hope one day you’ll be proud of the woman I’ve become, just like I’m endlessly proud to be your mom. You saved me in ways you’ll never fully understand. Happy Mother’s Day to all the mamas out there!
